summary: 0x7d5d4fff14c285c96810336fc661df1bca2dd15c - In the quirky world of Memeland, where every meme had a life of its own, there lived a particularly peculiar frog named PEEPEE. Unlike his fellow frogs, PEEPEE had a unique trait—he was always on the verge of peeing. He always wore a hat that said “Make PePE Great AGAIN”
